@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_fuazqv(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (wp.sin((v2 + 0.97 / v1 + 0.83)) * wp.abs(v1))
    v2 = wp.abs(wp.cos((tmp + 0.18 + v1 + 0.22)))
    tmp = v2
    v0 = v1
    data[tid] = v0
